  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.5,
    "endTime": 139.5,
    "text": "Yeah, you look sexy, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.5,
    "endTime": 140.5,
    "text": "You know I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.5,
    "endTime": 141.5,
    "text": "Watch out for that door."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.5,
    "endTime": 143.5,
    "text": "Yo, how much you benched?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.5,
    "endTime": 144.5,
    "text": "Seriously."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.5,
    "endTime": 145.5,
    "text": "All right, let's do this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.5,
    "endTime": 146.5,
    "text": "Who's got theories?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.5,
    "endTime": 148.5,
    "text": "Uh, alarm didn't go off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.5,
    "endTime": 150.5,
    "text": "All three alarms, all with battery backup?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.5,
    "endTime": 152.5,
    "text": "Come on, who wants to take this seriously?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.5,
    "endTime": 153.5,
    "text": "Ooh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.5,
    "endTime": 154.5,
    "text": "She was taken in her sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.5,
    "endTime": 155.5,
    "text": "That's what I'm talking about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.5,
    "endTime": 159.5,
    "text": "Super dark, Boyle, but way more plausible than the Sarge's idiotic alarm clock theory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.5,
    "endTime": 162.5,
    "text": "I bet she tucked herself into bed too tight and got stuck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.5,
    "endTime": 165.5,
    "text": "Maybe she fell into another dimension where she's interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.5,
    "endTime": 167.5,
    "text": "It's 9 a.m."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.5,
    "endTime": 168.5,
    "text": "Why is no one working?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.5,
    "endTime": 170.5,
    "text": "Amy Santiago is a few minutes late."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.5,
    "endTime": 172.5,
    "text": "And we're all trying to guess why."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.5,
    "endTime": 173.5,
    "text": "I like to play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.5,
    "endTime": 178.5,
    "text": "I'd say she's in line at the bank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.5,
    "endTime": 180.5,
    "text": "This is fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.5,
    "endTime": 182.5,
    "text": "It is fun, but you're all wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.5,
    "endTime": 187.5,
    "text": "She clearly slipped through a subway grade and is having terrible sex with a mole man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.5,
    "endTime": 189.5,
    "text": "There she is, Amy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.5,
    "endTime": 190.5,
    "text": "Where have you been?"
