  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.5,
    "endTime": 200.5,
    "text": "Santiago, you will tell us, and you will tell us now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.5,
    "endTime": 202.5,
    "text": "There was a problem at the bank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.5,
    "endTime": 203.5,
    "text": "Hot damn!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.5,
    "endTime": 204.5,
    "text": "This is the boat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.5,
    "endTime": 208.5,
    "text": "Now, Charles has to think we're totally sober and we solved his puzzle, so we good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.5,
    "endTime": 209.5,
    "text": "Yep, I'm drunk as hell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.5,
    "endTime": 210.5,
    "text": "That's not what I asked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.5,
    "endTime": 211.5,
