  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.5,
    "endTime": 214.5,
    "text": "I've seen you do enough of these harebrained schemes that are hard to play along."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.5,
    "endTime": 216.5,
    "text": "If Charles asks, what's wrong,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.5,
