    "startTime": 238.5,
    "endTime": 239.5,
    "text": "Nine and a half."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.5,
    "endTime": 240.5,
    "text": "Yet worse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.5,
    "endTime": 241.5,
    "text": "Anyway, here are my options."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.5,
    "endTime": 243.5,
    "text": "A, I keep pestering Romero to tell me where the drugs are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.5,
