    "text": "A little castrate-y."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.5,
    "endTime": 259.5,
    "text": "Yeah, that's what I keep bumping up against, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.5,
    "endTime": 261.5,
    "text": "Well, you know, whenever I'm backed into a corner,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.5,
    "endTime": 262.5,
    "text": "I just do what I do best."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.5,
    "endTime": 266.5,
    "text": "I drive across country, forge a new identity, and then take a job as a camp counselor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.5,
    "endTime": 267.5,
    "text": "Oh, my God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.5,
    "endTime": 268.5,
    "text": "Caleb, you're a genius."
