    "text": "All right, this is gonna be tough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.5,
    "endTime": 290.5,
    "text": "I'm really gonna have to thread the needle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.5,
    "endTime": 291.5,
    "text": "Ooh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.5,
    "endTime": 293.5,
    "text": "I got really good at threading needles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.5,
    "endTime": 295.5,
    "text": "Back when you were making your skin suit,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.5,
    "endTime": 296.5,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.5,
    "endTime": 300.5,
    "text": "Look, I like being friends with you, but you have to stop bringing that up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.5,
    "endTime": 301.5,
    "text": "But we're friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.5,
    "endTime": 302.5,
    "text": "I know I said"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.5,
