    "text": "Who told you that garbage?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.5,
    "endTime": 313.5,
    "text": "I was gonna say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.5,
    "endTime": 314.5,
    "text": "I love you, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.5,
    "endTime": 315.5,
    "text": "Amy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.5,
    "endTime": 316.5,
    "text": "Jake!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.5,
    "endTime": 319.5,
    "text": "David and I both arrived an hour early."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.5,
    "endTime": 321.5,
    "text": "We're sharing a French onion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.5,
    "endTime": 322.5,
    "text": "Mother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.5,
    "endTime": 325.5,
    "text": "You know how it is when you have a chance to bed an older woman."
  },
  {
